# Common Beginner Mistake

❌ Wrong:

```python
patient = 1

while patient <= 3:
    print(patient)
```

This never ends.

✅ Correct:

```python
patient = 1

while patient <= 3:
    print(patient)
    patient = patient + 1
```

Always update the loop variable.

